🔹 STEP 1: Create Custom VPC
Login → AWS Console
Search VPC
Click Create VPC
Select VPC only
Enter:
Name: Custom-VPC
IPv4 CIDR: 10.0.0.0/16
Click Create VPC
✔ VPC Created
🔹 STEP 2: Create Subnets
🟢 Create Public Subnet
Go to Subnets
Click Create subnet
Select Custom-VPC
Enter:
Name: Public-Subnet
AZ: us-east-1a (any one)
IPv4 CIDR: 10.0.1.0/24
Click Create
🔵 Create Private Subnet
Click Create subnet
Select Custom-VPC
Enter:
Name: Private-Subnet
Same AZ
IPv4 CIDR: 10.0.2.0/24
Click Create
✔ Both subnets created
🔹 STEP 3: Enable Public IP for Public Subnet
Go to Subnets
Select Public-Subnet
Click Actions → Edit subnet settings
Enable:
✔ Auto-assign Public IPv4
Save
❌ Do NOT enable for Private Subnet
🔹 STEP 4: Create Internet Gateway
Go to Internet Gateways
Click Create Internet Gateway
Name: Custom-IGW
Click Create
Attach IGW
Select IGW
Click Actions → Attach to VPC
Choose Custom-VPC
Click Attach
✔ IGW Attached
🔹 STEP 5: Create Route Table for Public Subnet
Go to Route Tables
Click Create route table
Name: Public-Route-Table
VPC: Custom-VPC
Create
Associate Public Subnet
Select Public-Route-Table
Click Subnet Associations
Edit → Select Public-Subnet
Save
Add Internet Route
Go to Routes
Click Edit routes
Add:
Destination: 0.0.0.0/0
Target: Internet Gateway → Custom-IGW
Save
✔ Public subnet now has internet
🔹 STEP 6: Launch Public EC2
Go to EC2 → Launch Instance
Name: Public-EC2
AMI: Ubuntu
Instance type: t3.micro
Key pair: select/create
Network Settings:
VPC: Custom-VPC
Subnet: Public-Subnet
Auto-assign Public IP: Enabled
Allow:
SSH (22)
HTTP (80)
HTTPS (443)
Click Launch
🔹 STEP 7: Launch Private EC2
Launch Instance again
Name: Private-EC2
Same AMI & type
Same key pair
Network Settings:
VPC: Custom-VPC
Subnet: Private-Subnet
Auto-assign Public IP: Disabled
Allow:
SSH (22)
HTTP (80)
HTTPS (443)
Click Launch
🔹 STEP 8: Test Connections
Connect to Public EC2
From terminal:
ssh -i key.pem ubuntu@<Public-IP>
✔ Works
Try Connecting to Private EC2
ssh -i key.pem ubuntu@10.0.2.177
❌ Output:
Connection timed out
✔ This is correct behavior
